'''雷蒙德·塞缪尔·汤姆林森'''（{{lang-en|'''Raymond Samuel Tomlinson'''}}，{{bd|1941年|4月23日|2016年|3月5日}}），暱稱'''雷·湯姆林森'''（{{lang|en|'''Ray Tomlinson'''}}），美国[[程序员|程序员]]，以发明电子邮件而知名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/mar/07/ray-tomlinson-email-inventor-and-selector-of-symbol-dies-aged-74|title=Ray Tomlinson, email inventor and selector of @ symbol, dies aged 74|work=the Guardian|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2021-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221085117/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2016/mar/07/ray-tomlinson-email-inventor-and-selector-of-symbol-dies-aged-74|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/3/6/11168718/ray-tomlinson-dead-inventor-of-email-obituary|title=Inventor of email and savior of the @ sign, Ray Tomlinson, is dead at 74|author=Dante D'Orazio|date=6 March 2016|publisher=Vox Media|work=The Verge|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2021-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427100218/https://www.theverge.com/2016/3/6/11168718/ray-tomlinson-dead-inventor-of-email-obituary|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/2016/03/06/469428062/ray-tomlinson-inventor-of-modern-email-has-died|title=Ray Tomlinson, Inventor Of Modern Email, Dies|date=6 March 2016|work=NPR.org|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027131742/https://www.npr.org/2016/03/06/469428062/ray-tomlinson-inventor-of-modern-email-has-died|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2016/03/06/email-inventor-ray-tomlinson-dies-aged-74/|title=Email inventor Ray Tomlinson dies aged 74|date=6 March 2016|work=The Telegraph|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212204514/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2016/03/06/email-inventor-ray-tomlinson-dies-aged-74/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/06/us/ray-tomlinson-email-creator-obit/|title=Ray Tomlinson, the creator of email, has died|author=Todd Leopold, CNN|date=6 March 2016|work=CNN|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108190928/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/06/us/ray-tomlinson-email-creator-obit/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/business-35741116|title=Email inventor Ray Tomlinson dies at 74|work=BBC News|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308052502/https://www.bbc.com/news/business-35741116|dead-url=no}}</ref>，被誉为“电子邮件之父”<ref name=":0" /><ref name="ori1">[http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20160307/bknint-20160307045700981-0307_17011_001.html 電郵之父74歲辭世　＠已成文化標誌] {{Wayback|url=http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20160307/bknint-20160307045700981-0307_17011_001.html |date=20190625013229 }} 東網即時，2016年3月7日</ref><ref name="wwp1">[http://news.wenweipo.com/2016/03/07/IN1603070018.htm 電郵之父湯姆林森離世:他命名@] {{Wayback|url=http://news.wenweipo.com/2016/03/07/IN1603070018.htm |date=20160309124041 }} 文匯網，2016年3月7日</ref>。

他于1971年在[[ARPANET|ARPANET]]系统上实现了第一个[[电子邮件|电子邮件]]系统<ref name="Internet Hall of Fame Bio" />。它是第一个能够在连接到ARPANE的不同主机用户之间发送邮件的系统。此前，邮件只能发送给使用同一台计算机的其他用户。 

为了实现这一目标，他用[[@|@]]符号将用户名与计算机名分隔，而这一方案在电子邮件地址中沿用至今<ref>{{cite web|url=http://openmap.bbn.com/~tomlinso/ray/firstemailframe.html|title=The First Network Email|author1=Ray Tomlinson|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060506003539/http://openmap.bbn.com/~tomlinso/ray/firstemailframe.html|archivedate=2006-05-06}}</ref>。 2012年獲選進入[[網際網路名人堂|網際網路名人堂]]。互联网名人堂评论道“汤姆林森的电子邮件程序带来了彻底的革命，从根本上改变人们的交流方式。”<ref name="Internet Hall of Fame Bio" />

== 早年生活与教育 ==
汤姆林森生于[[纽约州|纽约州]][[阿姆斯特丹_(纽约州)|阿姆斯特丹]]。但他的家人很快就搬到纽约州韦尔米尔斯的一个小村庄<ref name="New York Times">{{cite news |last=Grimes |first=William |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/08/technology/raymond-tomlinson-email-obituary.html |title=Raymond Tomlinson, Who Put the @ Sign in Email, Is Dead at 74 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=March 7, 2016 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308193247/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/08/technology/raymond-tomlinson-email-obituary.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。幼年的汤姆林森对一切机械的运转方式都非常着迷<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1440259|title=74岁电邮之父雷·汤姆林森离世：他让邮件有了@|accessdate=2016-03-07|author=|date=2016-03-07|publisher=澎湃新闻网|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610094613/http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1440259|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在{{Le|布罗达尔宾 (纽约州)|Broadalbin, New York|布罗达尔宾}}附近的布罗达尔宾中心学校上学<ref>{{cite news |last=Varghese |first=Sam |url=http://www.itwire.com/business-it-news/networking/71752-email-inventor-ray-tomlinson-dead-at-74.html |title=Email inventor Ray Tomlinson dead at 74 |work=iTWire |date=March 7, 2016 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228231223/https://www.itwire.com/business-it-news/networking/71752-email-inventor-ray-tomlinson-dead-at-74.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之后考入[[特洛伊_(纽约州)|特洛伊]]的[[伦斯勒理工学院|伦斯勒理工学院]]（RPI）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://m.ftchinese.com/story/001066503|title=“电子邮件之父”汤姆林森去世|accessdate=2015-03-07|author=|date=2015-03-07|publisher=FT中文网|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612174521/http://m.ftchinese.com/story/001066503|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在那里他参加了[[IBM|IBM]]的带薪实习项目。他于1963年获得了[[電機工程學|电气工程学]]学士学位<ref name="TechRepublic" />。

从RPI毕业后，他进入[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]继续他的电气工程教育。在MIT期间，汤姆林森曾在语音通信研究组工作，开发了一个模拟数字混合语音合成器，并以此作为他硕士论文课题。他在1965年获得电气工程硕士学位<ref name="New York Times" />。

== 生涯 ==
1967年，他加入了Bolt Beranek and Newman公司（[[BBN科技|BBN科技]]公司的前身），在那里他协助开发了[[TOPS-20|TENEX]]操作系统，在其上實作了[[ARPANET|ARPANET]][[网络控制程序|网络控制程序]]與[[telnet|telnet]]協定，並參與[[TCP/IP|TCP/IP]]協定的早期研發。他写了一个名为CPYNET的文件传输程序，其通过ARPANET进行文件传输<ref>{{cite book |last=Hafner |first1=Katie |last2=Lyon |first2=Matthew |title=Where Wizards Stay Up Late: The Origins Of The Internet |publisher=Simon and Schuster |year=1998 |page=191 |isbn=978-0684832678 |accessdate=March 8, 2016 }}</ref>。后来汤姆林森被要求修改一个名叫SNDMSG的程序，它可通过运行TENEX，向其他使用[[分時系統|分时系统]]的计算机用户发送实时消息<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.economist.com/news/science-and-technology/21694354-raymond-samuel-tomlinson-died-march-5th-aged-74-email-pioneer |title=Ray Tomlinson, who sent the first e-mail, has died |work=[[The_Economist|The Economist]] |date=March 7, 2016 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2017-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170608233919/http://www.economist.com/news/science-and-technology/21694354-raymond-samuel-tomlinson-died-march-5th-aged-74-email-pioneer |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他把CPYNET的一些代码添加到SNDMSG中，这样就可以把消息发送给使用其他计算机的用户，世界上第一封电子邮件由此诞生<ref>{{cite news |last=Kawamoto |first=Dawn |url=http://www.informationweek.com/software/creator-of-network-email-ray-tomlinson-dies/d/d-id/1324592 |title=Creator Of Network Email Ray Tomlinson Dies |work=InformationWeek |date=March 7, 2016 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225021844/https://www.informationweek.com/software/creator-of-network-email-ray-tomlinson-dies/d/d-id/1324592 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

汤姆林森发送的第一封电子邮件是一封测试邮件。它没有被保留下来，汤姆林森称其“微不足道”，就像“[[QWERTY键盘|QWERTYUIOP]]”一样。这通常被人们断章取义为“第一封电子邮件是QWERTYUIOP”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://openmap.bbn.com/~tomlinso/ray/mistakes.html|title=Frequently Made Mistakes|author1=Ray Tomlinson|access-date=2016-03-07|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301021534/http://openmap.bbn.com/~tomlinso/ray/mistakes.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 汤姆林森后来表示这些“文本信息已经完全忘记”<ref>{{cite news | url=http://thelede.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/05/04/internet-star-least-473-years-old/ | work=The New York Times | title=Internet Star @ Least 473 Years Old | first=Robert | last=Mackey | date=2009-05-04 | accessdate=2010-05-22 | archive-date=2021-01-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126210047/https://thelede.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/05/04/internet-star-least-473-years-old/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

起初，他的电子邮件收发系统被认为是不重要的。它的开发并非来自其老板的命令，汤姆林森追求它仅仅“因为它似乎是一个不错的主意”<ref name="New York Times" />。当汤姆林森给他的同事杰里·伯奇菲尔德（Jerry Burchfiel）看时，汤姆林森说“不要告诉任何人！这不是我们应该要做的工作。”<ref>{{cite magazine | url=http://www.forbes.com/asap/1998/1005/126.html | magazine=Forbes | date=October 5, 1998 | accessdate=February 2, 2016 | author=Sasha Cavender | title=Legends | archive-date=2020-08-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806141735/https://www.forbes.com/asap/1998/1005/126.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 逝世 ==
2016年3月5日，汤姆林森因[[心脏病|心脏病]]在[[麻薩諸塞州|麻薩諸塞州]]{{link-en|林肯 (麻薩諸塞州)|Lincoln, Massachusetts
|林肯}}的家中离世，享年74岁<ref name="TechRepublic">{{cite web|url=http://www.techrepublic.com/article/email-inventor-ray-tomlinson-dies-at-74/|title=Email inventor Ray Tomlinson dies at 74|author=Evan Koblentz|date=March 5, 2016|work=TechRepublic|access-date=2016-03-07|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421183949/https://www.techrepublic.com/article/email-inventor-ray-tomlinson-dies-at-74/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-35741116|title=Email inventor Ray Tomlinson dies at 74|work=BBC News|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108160552/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-35741116|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的僱主[[雷神公司|雷神公司]]證實他的死訊<ref name="ori1"/>。[[Google|Google]]旗下的[[Gmail|Gmail]]在社交網站[[Twitter|Twitter]]發文，感謝湯姆林森對電郵發展的貢獻<ref>[http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&itemid=858597 電子郵件之父湯姆林森病逝] {{Wayback|url=http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&itemid=858597 |date=20190610072827 }} 881903.com ，2016年3月7日</ref>。

