* 2001年，他荣获国际数字艺术与科学学院的[[威比奖|威比奖]]终身成就奖。同年，他入选伦斯勒校友名人堂（Rensselaer Alumni Hall of Fame）<ref name="Rensselaer Alumni Hall of Fame">{{cite web|title=Raymond S. Tomlinson: Inventor of Network Electronic Mail|url=http://www.rpi.edu/about/hof/tomlinson.html|website=Alumni Hall of Fame|publisher=Rensselaer|accessdate=6 March 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309215456/http://www.rpi.edu/about/hof/tomlinson.html|archivedate=2016-03-09}}</ref>。
* 2002年，《发现》杂志授予其创新奖<ref name="Internet Hall of Fame Bio" />。
